The paper deals with communication complexity, which is a topic in theoretical computer science and falls under the cs.CC (Computational Complexity) category. The use of block sensitivity and deterministic complexity suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) categories.
